@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
        <h1>About PdfPeaks</h1>
        <p class="lead">Empowering individuals and businesses with fast, secure, and free PDF tools — no installation required.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="about-content">
    <div class="container">

        <div class="about-block">
            <h2>Who We Are</h2>
            <p>
                PdfPeaks is a professional online platform dedicated to providing a comprehensive suite of PDF and image manipulation tools.
                We believe that powerful document processing should be accessible to everyone — without paywalls, software installations,
                or technical expertise. Our mission is to simplify the way people work with documents, one file at a time.
            </p>
            <p>
                Founded with a focus on usability, speed, and privacy, PdfPeaks serves individuals, students, professionals, and businesses
                across the globe. Whether you need to merge a few documents, compress a large file, or convert a PDF to Word in seconds,
                PdfPeaks has the right tool for the job.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-block">
            <h2>What We Offer</h2>
            <p>
                Our platform currently features over 25 tools spanning two core categories:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>PDF Tools:</strong> Merge, split, compress, rotate, unlock, protect, organize, edit, and convert PDFs to and from Word, Excel, PowerPoint, JPG, and PNG formats.</li>
                <li><strong>Image Tools:</strong> Resize, crop, rotate, flip, compress, convert between formats, and transform images into PDF documents.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                All tools are available directly in your browser — no account required for basic usage. We are continuously expanding our
                toolset based on user feedback and industry needs.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-block">
            <h2>Our Core Values</h2>
            <div class="values-grid">
                <div class="value-card">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-shield-alt me-2" style="color: var(--primary-color);"></i>Privacy First</h3>
                    <p>All uploaded files are automatically deleted from our servers immediately after processing. We do not store, share, or analyse your documents.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="value-card">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-bolt me-2" style="color: var(--secondary-color);"></i>Speed & Reliability</h3>
                    <p>Our infrastructure is optimised for fast processing. Most operations complete in seconds, regardless of file size.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="value-card">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-gift me-2" style="color: var(--accent-color);"></i>Free for Everyone</h3>
                    <p>Our core tools are completely free with no hidden fees, subscription traps, or usage limits designed to push upgrades.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="value-card">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-globe me-2" style="color: #20c997;"></i>Accessibility</h3>
                    <p>We are committed to making our platform accessible across all devices, operating systems, and browsers — no software installation required.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-block">
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <p>
                We welcome feedback, questions, and partnership enquiries. If you have a suggestion for a new tool, encountered an issue,
                or simply want to get in touch, please visit our <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Contact">Contact page</a>.
            </p>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>
